{"thig5.2:0.1":"Therigatha 5.2 ","thig5.2:0.2":"Pancakanipata ","thig5.2:0.3":"Vimalatherigatha ","thig5.2:1.1":"“Matta vannena rupena, ","thig5.2:1.2":"sobhaggena yasena ca; ","thig5.2:1.3":"Yobbanena cupatthaddha, ","thig5.2:1.4":"annasamatimanniham. ","thig5.2:2.1":"Vibhusetva imam kayam, ","thig5.2:2.2":"sucittam balalapanam; ","thig5.2:2.3":"Atthasim vesidvaramhi, ","thig5.2:2.4":"luddo pasamivoddiya. ","thig5.2:3.1":"Pilandhanam vidamsenti, ","thig5.2:3.2":"guyham pakasikam bahum; ","thig5.2:3.3":"Akasim vividham mayam, ","thig5.2:3.4":"ujjagghanti bahum janam. ","thig5.2:4.1":"Sajja pindam caritvana, ","thig5.2:4.2":"munda sanghatiparuta; ","thig5.2:4.3":"Nisinna rukkhamulamhi, ","thig5.2:4.4":"avitakkassa labhini. ","thig5.2:5.1":"Sabbe yoga samucchinna, ","thig5.2:5.2":"ye dibba ye ca manusa; ","thig5.2:5.3":"Khepetva asave sabbe, ","thig5.2:5.4":"sitibhutamhi nibbuta”ti. ","thig5.2:6.1":"… Vimala puranaganika theri …. "}